{{Top|leg}}
A '''traladon''' was an animal popular in [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] food.

Several by-products of the Traladon were very popular. [[Traladon ribs]] with special sauce was often a favorite for barbecues, as well as [[traladon steak]] and [[traladon goulash]]. Traladon [[Traladon milk|milk]] was popular for adding to [[vine-coffeine]], and [[traladon cheese]] was a great appetizer. [[Traladon and tuber stew]], on the other hand, was not a popular dish.

The phrase "don't look a gift traladon in the mouth" was used throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], meaning that one should not question or critically inspect something that is given to him or her as a gift.

